    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>parsnip[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then slice</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced parsnip</strong> to a heatproof bowl</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1689771379871-x200.jpg",
