          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once tender, add the <strong>cooked parsnip</strong> to the pan with your <strong>'Nduja </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1689771391862-x200.jpg",
