            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>drained orzo </strong>with<strong> half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian cheese </strong>(save some for a garnish!)</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>'Nduja & creamy parsnip orzo</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
