            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>'Nduja & creamy parsnip orzo </strong>and top with the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar </strong>and a little<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining grated Italian cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
